'''''Arnoldi Chronica Slavorum''''' is the continuation of [[Helmold]]'s ''[[Chronica Slavorum]]'' by [[Arnold of Lübeck]].<ref>Iben Fonnesberg-Schmidt, ''The Popes and the Baltic Crusades: 1147-1254'', (Brill, 2007), 13.</ref> It was continued down to 1209.
